pullRequest.title: Add release notes for 0.244
pullRequest.bodyText:
Missing Release Notes
Daniel Ohayon

 #15316 Fix caching and case-sensitivity issues with enum type signatures (Merged by: Rongrong Zhong)

Mohamed Shafee

 #15338 Change warning to ignore unreadable partitions to be a digest (Merged by: James Sun)

Rongrong Zhong

 af78e1b Chage Block's toString to be unique with respect to hashCode
 f439df5 Fix LambdaDefinitionExpression canonicalization

Sergii Druzkin

 #15286 Enable reading of FileStatistics in presto-orc (Merged by: Rebecca Schlussel)
 #15286 Enable reading of FileStatistics in presto-orc (Merged by: Rebecca Schlussel)

Extracted Release Notes

#15213 (Author: James Petty): Improve nested loop operator performance

Improve performance of NestedLoopJoinOperator.


#15213 (Author: James Petty): Improve nested loop operator performance

Improve performance of NestedLoopJoinOperator.


#15303 (Author: Ariel Weisberg): Prefer verifier cluster memory limits

Improve verifier handling of memory limits by using the limits from the verifier cluster which are frequently better matched to the queries picked to be run in the verifier suite.


#15319 (Author: Xiang Fu): Pinot streaming connector

Support query Pinot server with streaming API (Requires Pinot Version >= 0.6.0.).
Enabled it by setting pinot.use-streaming-for-segment-queries=true.


#15323 (Author: Ariel Weisberg): Add peak node total memory to statistics

Add peak_node_total_memory to statistics to allow monitoring the peak sum of memory used across tasks at any node by a query.


#15323 (Author: Ariel Weisberg): Add peak node total memory to statistics

Add peak_node_total_memory to statistics to allow monitoring the peak sum of memory used across tasks at any node by a query.


#15332 (Author: Adli Mousa): Fix druid reading issue

Fix druid reading issue.


#15332 (Author: Adli Mousa): Fix druid reading issue

Fix druid reading issue.


#15332 (Author: Adli Mousa): Fix druid reading issue

Fix druid reading issue.


#15341 (Author: Leiqing Cai): Emit session properties in VerifierQueryEvent

Add control and test session properties to Verifier output.


#15342 (Author: Leiqing Cai): [Verifier] Fix JDBC URL selection

Fix an issue where queries are always directed to the first cluster when multiple control or test clusters are specified.


#15347 (Author: Shixuan Fan): Fix hamming_distance to handle code point zero

Fix hamming_distance to handle code point zero correctly.


#15350 (Author: Ajay George): Add Thrift transport support for TaskStatus

Add thrift transport support for TaskStatus which can be enabled using config property experimental.internal-communication.thrift-transport-enabled.


#15355 (Author: James Petty): Add SDK and API metrics to GlueHiveMetastore

Add support for AWS SDK client request metrics and Glue API metrics to GlueHiveMetastore.


#15383 (Author: Rebecca Schlussel): Make encryption key explicit when reading DWRF stripes

Fix a bug with reading encrypted DWRF tables where queries could fail with a NullPointerException.


#15383 (Author: Rebecca Schlussel): Make encryption key explicit when reading DWRF stripes

Fix a bug with reading encrypted DWRF tables where queries could fail with a NullPointerException.


#15403 (Author: Rebecca Schlussel): Fix int overflow error when spilling large page

Fix an issue where queries could encounter an int overflow error during spilling.


#15405 (Author: Rebecca Schlussel): Fix local exchanges when materializing remote exchanges

Add support for spilling joins when using materialized exchanges.

@@ -0,0 +1,48 @@
+=============
+Release 0.244
+=============
+
+**Highlights**
+==============
+* Improve performance of NestedLoopJoinOperator.
+* Add support for spilling joins when using materialized exchanges.
+
+
+**Details**
+===========
+
+General Changes
+_______________
+* Fix an issue where queries could encounter an int overflow error during spilling.
+* Fix hamming_distance to handle code point zero correctly.
+* Fix caching and case-sensitivity bugs with type signatures for enum types.
+* Fix LambdaDefinitionExpression canonicalization to correctly canonicalize Block constant (:issue:15424).
+* Improve performance of NestedLoopJoinOperator.
+* Add `peak_node_total_memory` to statistics to allow monitoring the peak sum of memory used across tasks at any node by a query.
+* Add support for spilling joins when using materialized exchanges.
+* Add thrift transport support for TaskStatus which can be enabled using config property ``experimental.internal-communication.thrift-transport-enabled``.
+
+Verifier Changes
+________________
+* Fix an issue where queries are always directed to the first cluster when multiple control or test clusters are specified.
+* Improve verifier handling of memory limits by using the limits from the verifier cluster which are frequently better matched to the queries picked to be run in the verifier suite.
+* Add control and test session properties to Verifier output.
+
+Druid Changes
+_____________
+* Fix druid reading issue.
+
+Hive Changes
+____________
+* Fix a bug with reading encrypted DWRF tables where queries could fail with a NullPointerException.
+* Add support for AWS SDK client request metrics and Glue API metrics to GlueHiveMetastore.
+
+Pinot Changes
+_____________
+* Enabled it by setting `pinot.use-streaming-for-segment-queries=true`.
